==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water beetle
<hw>Wa"ter bee"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of
numerous species of aquatic beetles belonging to <gen>Dytiscus</gen> and
allied genera of the family <fam>Dytiscidae</fam>, and to various genera
of the family <fam>Hydrophilidae</fam>. These beetles swim with great
agility, the fringed hind legs acting together like oars.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water bellows</ent>⟦br⟧
